	

	git init.
	
	git config user.name "user name".

	git config user. Mail "email" . 

	git status  => to view current status of repo.
	
	git add file => to add to git repo.

	git add . => to add all files in repo.

	git commit-m "commit message" => to save changes in repo.

	git log => commit history.

	git branch => to list branches in repo.

	git branch branchname => to create new branch

	git checkout branch name / commit id => to move to that specified branch or commit.

	git diff => to see the difference before adding.

	git stash => to hide code from latest changes.

	git stash list => to view the list of hidden code.

  	git stash pop => to unhide the code stashed.

	git mv old name   new name => to rename a file
